{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260420055414","title":"Satu keputusan per ADR menjaga batasan dan riwayat yang bersih","desc":"Setiap ADR harus meng-cover satu keputusan signifikan agar log keputusan tetap granular, fokus, dan mudah ditelusuri.","tags":["permanent-note","architecture","adr","documentation"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260420055414","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"bdcc20a0972fa55103069b9abbffc72a","updated":1776683200279,"created":1776683200279,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055414","id":"zettel.20260420055414","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055414","id":"zettel.20260420055414","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.architecture","alias":"architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055414","id":"zettel.20260420055414","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.adr","alias":"adr","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.adr"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055414","id":"zettel.20260420055414","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.documentation","alias":"documentation","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.documentation"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055414","id":"zettel.20260420055414","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":18,"offset":761},"end":{"line":16,"column":69,"offset":812},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":3,"offset":1553},"end":{"line":27,"column":28,"offset":1578},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055414"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records","id":"zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":49,"column":3,"offset":2296},"end":{"line":49,"column":28,"offset":2321},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055414"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":3,"offset":767},"end":{"line":19,"column":28,"offset":792},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420055414"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"satu-keputusan-per-adr-menjaga-batasan-dan-riwayat-yang-bersih\">Satu keputusan per ADR menjaga batasan dan riwayat yang bersih<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#satu-keputusan-per-adr-menjaga-batasan-dan-riwayat-yang-bersih\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Satu ADR = satu keputusan. Jika satu dokumen memuat banyak keputusan, batasan hilang, diskusi jadi kabur, dan riwayat perubahan susah dilacak.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ADR yang menggulung banyak keputusan ke dalam satu file merusak sifatnya sebagai unit keputusan.</li>\n<li>Ketika satu keputusan berubah, sulit menentukan apakah ADR masih valid atau perlu supersede.</li>\n<li>Format file terpisah dengan nama deskriptif membuat katalog keputusan bisa dipindai cepat.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Perlu disiplin memilih level keputusan: hanya yang signifikan layak di-ADR-kan.</li>\n<li>Penamaan file harus mencerminkan keputusan agar tim bisa membaca daftar ADR tanpa membuka semua file.</li>\n<li>Granularitas ADR membantu memisahkan diskusi teknis menjadi topik yang lebih mudah di-review.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>→ Dikuatkan oleh <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records\">Architecture Decision Record — Martin Fowler</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">adr (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">documentation (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.architecture-decision-records\">Architecture Decision Record — Martin Fowler</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsC